{"tid":1331404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721]18區直線街貼遊擊 721集氣街招     [琴晚多圖]  [魔鬼式文宣]","createTime":"2019-07-19T02:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T09:45:40.000Z","uid":278361,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1c09d269eb6fdaca99aa4eec63333bedb86d8f04","tid":1331404,"uid":278361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n我地發動緊18區 直線派傳單/街招遊擊 集氣叫同路人一定要出黎<br />\n要自己區每支燈柱 同電箱都有<br />\n<br />\n【銀髮族】長者不懂上連登靠連儂牆收資訊 斥警方報細數︰我哋加埋都百萬歲啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1328917/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1328917/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家入黎先填表 填完自己PIN多次<br />\n填完可以搵返自己果區既人一齊夾時間地點<br />\n大家可以先派傳單後貼街招<br />\n<br />\n方法:<br />\n1. 五金鋪噴膠 (最快最易但要有技術噴得平均)<br />\n2. 白膠漿水/膠水 (要買小水桶油掃 油掃愈大愈好 同A4一樣橫 最好係面掃多次)<br />\n3. AB膠 (黃金利器 係面掃多次痴完第日變左水晶)<br />\n1-2 人睇水 1人鬆膠 1人貼<br />\n已經防到哂藍絲同警<br />\n3-4個人已經可以搞一區!!!!.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意幫手 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LlZPuBc5mvMvvkXUetr0xA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLlZPuBc5mvMvvkXUetr0xA&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=957f637f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LlZPuBc5mvMvvkXUetr0xA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴晚已有<br />\n觀塘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qk0ae1A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQk0ae1A.jpg&h=68405de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMC71GA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMC71GA.jpg&h=0fe17faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKJWaz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKJWaz2.jpg&h=5c5233e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柴灣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiLhEva.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiLhEva.jpg&h=a0f473f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太古<br />\